    {
      "id": "1924750c-f3ba-8002-a9c4-fcf06ad6e744",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Automated group formation remains a key challenge for educators wishing to implement collaborative learning pedagogical activities. The authors propose a genetic algorithm that strives for personality trait homogeneity. The authors perform an experiment with 132 students using the Big 5 framework. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1924750c-f3ba-8002-a9c4-fcf06ad6e744",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
