              "text": {
                "content": "Automated group formation remains a key challenge for educators wishing to implement collaborative learning pedagogical activities. The authors propose a genetic algorithm that strives for personality trait homogeneity. The authors perform an experiment with 132 students using the Big 5 framework. ",
